  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4ac5db028c269c8409af5fc2483630e8, type: 3}
  m_Name: ChapterLocalizationTable
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ChapterLocalizationTable
  rows:
  - Language_ID: 15000
    KR: "\uBC14\uB2E4\uC758 \uC804\uC124: \uC544\uD2C0\uB77C"
    EN: Myth of the Atla
  - Language_ID: 15001
    KR: "\uC655\uAD81 \uBC29\uBB38"
    EN: Visit the Palace
  - Language_ID: 15002
    KR: "\uC544\uD2C0\uB77C\uC758 \uACFC\uAC70"
    EN: The Tale of Atla
  - Language_ID: 15003
    KR: "\uB2E4\uC2DC \uC2DC\uC791\uB41C \uD0D0\uC0AC "
    EN: Re-Voyage
  - Language_ID: 15004
    KR: "\uBC94\uB78C\uC758 \uADFC\uC6D0"
    EN: Seek Overflow
  - Language_ID: 15006
    KR: "\uD0DC\uD48D\uC758 \uB208: \uC5D0\uC624\uD504"
    EN: Eye of the Eof
  - Language_ID: 15007
    KR: "\uD0DC\uD48D\uC758 \uBFCC\uB9AC"
    EN: Storm's Root
  - Language_ID: 15008
    KR: "\uC2E0\uC758 \uAE30\uC801?"
    EN: God's Miracle?
  - Language_ID: 15009
    KR: "\uC778\uAC04\uC758 \uB9C8\uBC95"
    EN: Human Magic
  - Language_ID: 15010
    KR: "\uC88B\uC740 \uB9C8\uBC95\uC0AC"
    EN: Good Wizard
  - Language_ID: 15012
    KR: "\uC6A9\uAC10\uD55C \uB3C4\uB9C8\uBC40: \uC5D4\uB514\uC544"
    EN: Lizard-Endia
  - Language_ID: 15013
    KR: "\uC0AC\uB77C\uC9C4 \uC601\uC6C5"
    EN: The Lost Hero
  - Language_ID: 15014
    KR: "\uAE30\uB85D\uC744 \uCC3E\uC544\uC11C"
    EN: Find the Records
  - Language_ID: 15015
    KR: "\uAD6C\uB984 \uD6D4\uCE58\uAE30"
    EN: Stea a Cloud
  - Language_ID: 15016
    KR: "\uC0AC\uAC74\uC758 \uC9C4\uC0C1"
    EN: Truth Reveal
  - Language_ID: 15017
    KR: "\uC9C4\uC2E4\uC744 \uD5A5\uD574\uC11C"
    EN: Toward the Truth
  - Language_ID: 15019
    KR: "\uC6A9\uACFC \uC6A9\uC0AC: \uB4DC\uB77C\uCF54"
    EN: Drake Pupil Draco
  - Language_ID: 15020
    KR: "\uC774\uBBF8 \uBC1D\uD600\uC9C4 \uC9C4\uC2E4"
    EN: Revealed Truth
  - Language_ID: 15021
    KR: "\uB85C\uB4DC\uC640\uC758 \uB9CC\uB0A8"
    EN: Meeting the Lord
  - Language_ID: 15022
    KR: "\uC5D0\uD544\uB85C\uADF8\uAC00 \uC544\uB2CC \uC774\uC57C\uAE30"
    EN: Not an Epilogue
  - Language_ID: 15023
    KR: "\uC5D0\uC774\uD504\uB9B4\uC758 \uC2A4\uC2B9"
    EN: April's Master
  - Language_ID: 15024
    KR: "\uB118\uACA8\uC57C\uD558\uB294 \uB9C8\uC9C0\uB9C9 \uC7A5"
    EN: Face the End
  - Language_ID: 16000
    KR: "\uC5D0\uC774\uD504\uB9B4\uC758 \uCCAB \uBC88\uC9F8 \uB3D9\uD654."
    EN: April's First Fairy Tale.
  - Language_ID: 16001
    KR: "\uB798\uB9AC\uC758 \uC808\uCE5C\uC740 \uC5B4\uB514\uC5D0...?"
    EN: Where is Larry's BFF...?
  - Language_ID: 16002
    KR: "\uC544\uD2C0\uB77C\uC5D0\uB294 \uACFC\uAC70\uC5D4 \uC5B4\uB5A4 \uC77C\uC774."
    EN: This is the story of what happened to Atla.
  - Language_ID: 16003
    KR: "\uC624\uC154\uC758 \uC548\uB0B4\uB97C \uBC1B\uC544 \uB530\uB77C\uAC04\uB2E4."
    EN: Follow along under Osher's guidance...
  - Language_ID: 16004
    KR: "\uBB34\uC5C7\uC774 \uBC94\uB78C\uC758 \uC6D0\uC778\uC77C\uAE4C."
    EN: What is causing the Overflow..?
  - Language_ID: 16006
    KR: "\uAC11\uC791\uC2A4\uB808 \uD558\uB298\uB85C"
    EN: Suddenly into the sky.
  - Language_ID: 16007
    KR: "\uC5D0\uC624\uD504\uC5D4 \uBB34\uC2A8 \uC5B4\uB5A4 \uB3D9\uD654\uAC00?"
    EN: What fairy tale is told in Eof?
  - Language_ID: 16008
    KR: "\uC5D0\uC624\uD504\uC5D4 \uC5C4\uCCAD\uB09C \uB9C8\uBC95\uC9C4\uC774."
    EN: The massive magic circle floating above Eof
  - Language_ID: 16009
    KR: "\uB125\uC2A4\uB294 \uC65C \uB9C8\uBC95\uC744...?"
    EN: Why is Nex so interested in magic?
  - Language_ID: 16010
    KR: "\uACC4\uD68D\uB300\uB85C \uD558\uB298\uB85C"
    EN: Into the sky, just as planned.
  - Language_ID: 16012
    KR: "\uBC88\uAC1C \uC18D\uC73C\uB85C."
    EN: Into the lightning.
  - Language_ID: 16013
    KR: "\uC218\uD638\uC790\uAC00 \uC5C6\uB2E4\uB2C8..?"
    EN: There is no guardian?
  - Language_ID: 16014
    KR: "\uCC45\uC5D4 \uB2F5\uC774 \uC788\uB2E4."
    EN: The answers lie within the books.
  - Language_ID: 16015
    KR: "\uD0DC\uD48D\uB3C4 \uD6D4\uCCE4\uC5C8\uB294\uB370, \uBB58."
    EN: I've even stolen a typhoon before, after all.
  - Language_ID: 16016
    KR: "\uB4DC\uB514\uC5B4 \uB9C8\uC8FC\uD55C \uBC94\uC778"
    EN: Finally, the culprit stands before you.
  - Language_ID: 16017
    KR: "\uCE5C\uAD6C\uB97C \uC704\uD574."
    EN: For the sake of a friend.
  - Language_ID: 16019
    KR: "\uC6A9\uC744 \uB354 \uC54C\uACE0 \uC2F6\uC5B4?"
    EN: Do you want to know more about dragons?
  - Language_ID: 16020
    KR: "\uB3D9...\uB3D9\uD654\uB77C\uB2C8 \uBB34\uC2A8\uC774\uC57C\uAE30\uC2DC\uC8E0?"
    EN: A f...fairy tale? What do you mean by that?
  - Language_ID: 16021
    KR: "\uC5ED\uC2DC \uC774\uC57C\uAE30\uB294 \uC6B0\uB450\uBA38\uB9AC\uC5D0\uAC8C."
    EN: It's always best to talk straight to the leader.
  - Language_ID: 16022
    KR: "\uADF8\uB7FC \uC6B0\uB9B0 \uC5B4\uB5BB\uAC8C \uD574\uC57C \uD574?"
    EN: So, what should we do now?
  - Language_ID: 16023
    KR: "\uC2A4\uC2B9\uB2D8\uC740 \uAC00\uBA74\uC744 \uBC97\uACE0 \uC815\uCCB4\uB97C..."
    EN: Uncover the truth behind the master's mask.
  - Language_ID: 16024
    KR: "\uC5B8\uC820\uAC00 \uB9C8\uC8FC\uD574\uC57C\uD558\uB294 \uC21C\uAC04."
    EN: A moment that must be faced someday.
